Moreover, to some people - like yourself, apparently - the idea of having sex is as abhorrent as not having sex is for promiscuous people. The idea that the culture you happen to live in predominantly deems your behaviour more virtuous than the latter is purely accidental and doesn't make you any more virtuous than a nimphomaniac or a satyriasist. But I'm glad it makes you feel happy. Just don't assume you are in a moral high ground because you got geographically lucky. And while I am undoubtedly a disgusting piece of shit, I'm not an ignorant piece of shit. You, on the other hand, are. You should try being more promiscuous in your reading. Abstinence in that regard is definitely not working out for ya.

